  "You are a star!\n\nEvery day, recognise something you have done well. Reward yourself with something that makes you happy. And take a deep breath to relax.":
    "Uyiqhawe!\n\nNsuku zonke, qaphela into oyenze kahle. Zivuze ngento ekwenza ujabule. Udonse umoya ukuze uzole.",
